version_description: Metallica is back with a wicked new album and this is the first chord sheet for this song off the new album. its in standard tuning. ROCK ON.
There is only one chord version of this song previously and this one i slightly simpler to play and contains the entire lyrics.
Chords only, simplified with correct places to hit each chord.
other chords (correct writing for getting akkord diagrams), better line
Metallica is back. this is the first chord sheet for this song and it's standard tuning plus No capo is needed.

Intermediates will learn Tab, this one is for novices so they could enjoy playing their favourite song. I added some 'intermediate parts' though, so you can increase the level with few licks when getting familiar.
Simple chords for acoustic guitar. Can be played along the recorded version.
This version is from SnM , Enjoy.
